videos.description: John Collins soars way above the rim for a huge alley oop to extend the WAKE FOREST run to 8-0
videos.headline: John Collins throws down the alley oop

videos.description: WAKE FOREST turnover leads to Joel Berry II throwing down the dunk
videos.headline: Joel Berry II hammers home the dunk on the break

videos.description: Isaiah Hicks throws it down after being left open under the hoop
videos.headline: Isaiah Hicks throws down the two-handed jam

videos.description: Tony Bradley appears to suffer head injury after his head/neck collided with Konstantinos Mitoglou
videos.headline: Tony Bradley appears to suffer head injury after collision

videos.description: Nate Britt buries a three to give NC a 13-point lead
videos.headline: Nate Britt buries the three

videos.description: A mistake by WAKE FOREST on defense leads to Kennedy Meeks' wide-open buzzer beater and pushes the NC lead to 15 at the half
videos.headline: Kennedy Meeks converts wide-open layup to beat the buzzer

videos.description: WAKE FOREST gets out on the break off the rebound, leads to quick three from Mitchell  Wilbekin
videos.headline: Mitchell Wilbekin knocks down wide open three in transition

videos.description: Brandon Childress drives and gets the layup to cut the NC lead to 3
videos.headline: Brandon Childress  drives and gets the layup

videos.description: Keyshawn Woods converts the tough layup and cuts the NC lead to 1
videos.headline: Keyshawn Woods takes it to the rack

videos.description: Brandon Childress drives and makes a ridiculous layup, draws the foul.
videos.headline: Brandon Childress converts and extremely tough and-one layup

videos.description: Keyshawn Woods goes hard at Nate Britt, draws the foul and gets the basket
videos.headline: Keyshawn Woods drives the lane for the and-one layup

videos.description: All five starters for No. 11 North Carolina score in double figures in a 93-87 win over Wake Forest.
videos.headline: UNC holds off charge to beat Wake Forest
